<h1 id="overlay-title">Friendship is Magic!</h1>
<p id="overlay-descrip" class="_pmvv-vidbox-descTxt">
Twilight Sparkle and her newfound friends obtain the Elements of Harmony and defeat Nightmare Moon.	</p>
<div class="rating-row" data-video-id="mwqqbo">
